---
title: Group Module - User Flow Diagram
description: Complete user flow for group management features
date: 07-03-26
---

flowchart TD
    Start([User Logs In]) --> CheckGroups{Has Groups?}
    
    %% Create New Group Flow
    CheckGroups -->|No| CreateGroup[Create New Group]
    CreateGroup --> EnterDetails[Enter Group Details<br/>Name, Description,<br/>Max Members]
    EnterDetails --> SetVisibility[Set Visibility<br/>Private/Public]
    SetVisibility --> SubmitGroup[Submit Group]
    SubmitGroup --> GroupCreated[Group Created ✅]
    GroupCreated --> OwnerRole[User Becomes Owner]
    OwnerRole --> InviteMembers[Invite Members]
    
    %% Existing Groups Flow
    CheckGroups -->|Yes| ViewGroups[View My Groups]
    ViewGroups --> SelectGroup{Select Action}
    
    %% View Group Details
    SelectGroup -->|View| ViewDetails[View Group Details<br/>Members, Tasks,<br/>Statistics]
    ViewDetails --> Dashboard[Group Dashboard]
    
    %% Invite Members
    SelectGroup -->|Invite| InviteFlow[Invite Members]
    InviteFlow --> ChooseMethod{Invite Method}
    ChooseMethod -->|Email| SendEmailInvite[Send Email Invitation]
    ChooseMethod -->|Link| GenerateLink[Generate Invite Link]
    ChooseMethod -->|Direct| AddDirectly[Add Directly]
    SendEmailInvite --> InviteSent[Invite Sent ✅]
    GenerateLink --> LinkShared[Link Shared ✅]
    AddDirectly --> MemberAdded[Member Added ✅]
    
    %% Member Actions
    SelectGroup -->|Manage Members| ManageMembers[Manage Members]
    ManageMembers --> MemberAction{Select Action}
    MemberAction -->|Promote| PromoteMember[Promote to Admin]
    MemberAction -->|Remove| RemoveMember[Remove Member]
    MemberAction -->|Change Role| ChangeRole[Change Role]
    PromoteMember --> RoleUpdated[Role Updated ✅]
    RemoveMember --> MemberRemoved[Member Removed ✅]
    ChangeRole --> RoleChanged[Role Changed ✅]
    
    %% Group Settings
    SelectGroup -->|Settings| GroupSettings[Group Settings]
    GroupSettings --> SettingAction{Update Setting}
    SettingAction -->|Name| UpdateName[Update Group Name]
    SettingAction -->|Description| UpdateDesc[Update Description]
    SettingAction -->|Visibility| UpdateVisibility[Update Visibility]
    SettingAction -->|Max Members| UpdateMax[Update Max Members]
    UpdateName --> SettingsSaved[Settings Saved ✅]
    UpdateDesc --> SettingsSaved
    UpdateVisibility --> SettingsSaved
    UpdateMax --> SettingsSaved
    
    %% Leave Group
    SelectGroup -->|Leave| LeaveGroup[Leave Group]
    LeaveGroup --> ConfirmLeave{Confirm?}
    ConfirmLeave -->|Yes| ProcessLeave[Process Leave]
    ProcessLeave --> CheckOwner{Is Owner?}
    CheckOwner -->|Yes| TransferOwnership[Transfer Ownership<br/>or Delete Group]
    CheckOwner -->|No| MemberLeft[Member Left ✅]
    TransferOwnership --> NewOwner[New Owner Assigned]
    NewOwner --> MemberLeft
    ConfirmLeave -->|No| CancelLeave[Cancel]
    
    %% Delete Group
    SelectGroup -->|Delete| DeleteGroup[Delete Group]
    DeleteGroup --> CheckPermission{Is Owner?}
    CheckPermission -->|No| PermissionDenied[Permission Denied ❌]
    CheckPermission -->|Yes| ConfirmDelete{Confirm Delete?}
    ConfirmDelete -->|Yes| ProcessDelete[Delete Group<br/>Archive Data]
    ProcessDelete --> GroupDeleted[Group Deleted ✅]
    ConfirmDelete -->|No| CancelDelete[Cancel]
    
    %% Task Integration
    Dashboard --> TaskAction{Task Action}
    TaskAction -->|Create| CreateTask[Create Group Task]
    TaskAction -->|View| ViewTasks[View Group Tasks]
    TaskAction -->|Assign| AssignTask[Assign to Members]
    CreateTask --> TaskCreated[Task Created ✅]
    ViewTasks --> TaskList[Task List Displayed]
    AssignTask --> TaskAssigned[Task Assigned ✅]
    
    %% Notifications
    InviteSent --> Notification[Send Notification]
    MemberAdded --> Notification
    RoleUpdated --> Notification
    SettingsSaved --> Notification
    Notification --> NotifyUsers[Notify Affected Users]
    
    %% Styling
    style Start fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style GroupCreated fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style InviteSent fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style MemberAdded fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style RoleUpdated fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style SettingsSaved fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style MemberLeft fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style GroupDeleted fill:#F44336,color:#fff
    style PermissionDenied fill:#FF9800,color:#fff
    style TaskCreated fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
    style TaskAssigned fill:#4CAF50,color:#fff
